<br />
<br />Oh, but not all hope is lost! I still have to beat FF Mystic Quest (FF USA, I believe, in Japan). But I don't think I'll be getting a PS3 or any of the next gen consoles; I'll probably have to upgrade its graphics card or something in a couple of years  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /> .

		

